                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote>
                        <locus>Folios 1v-2r</locus>: text in cloud bands on gold
								background, illuminated polychrome headpiece, margins decorated with
								gold floral design. 
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
